/radiomanager/status<pre><code>{
"radios": [
{
"status":"ESPNOW @ CH1",
"counters":"[4919TX/0RX] [0CRC/0SIZE/0VAL]",
"enabled":true
},
{
"status":"LoRa SX128X @ 2400.00MHz (10dBm)",
"counters":"[4919TX/0RX] [0CRC/0SIZE/0VAL]",
"enabled":true
}
]
}
</code></pre> <ul> <li><code>radios</code>: list of radios on the system</li> <li><code>status</code>: short radio-specific status string</li> <li><code>counters</code>: number of packets transmitted, received, and rejected for the 3 reasons listed (bad CRC, bad size, failed validation)</li> <li><code>enabled</code>: whether or not the radio is enabled</li> </ul>
